title: BRIEF-Keyrus H1 net income group share up at 1.7 million euros

BRIEF-Keyrus H1 net income group share up at 1.7 million euros Sept 21 
Sept 21 Keyrus SA : 
* H1 current operating income 3.1 million euros ($3.5 million) versus 2.3 million euros year ago 
* H1 net income group share 1.7 million euros versus 0.6 million euros year ago Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8938 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
